{"noun":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/b9/a7/102504_crt_8VG0C.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/b9/a7/102504_crt_8VG0C.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/b9/a7/102504_crt_8VG0C.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/b9/a7/102504_crt_8VG0C.jpg"},"name":"Starscream","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/fe/96/4167_prsn_iQprj.jpg?r=1514286894","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/fe/96/4167_prsn_iQprj.jpg?r=1514286894","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/fe/96/4167_prsn_iQprj.jpg?r=1514286894","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/fe/96/4167_prsn_iQprj.jpg?r=1514286894"},"name":"飛田展男","short_summary":"飛田 展男（とびた のぶお、1959年11月6日 - ）は、日本の声優、ナレーターであり、舞台俳優。アーツビジョン所属。\r\n茨城県水戸市出身。水戸市立三の丸小学校、茨城中学校・高等学校卒業。駒澤大学文学部歴史学科中退。体重55kg。血液型はAB型。愛称は「飛ちゃん」。\r\n\r\n飞田展男，可以说是日本男声优中的“变色龙”。他的角色反差极大，最为夸张的对比就是《安琪莉可》中的水之守护圣卢米埃和《烈火之炎》中的土门，一个美一个丑，一个柔弱一个健壮，一个温柔一个暴躁，一个优雅一个粗鲁，简直就是两个极端，令人怎么也无法相信这是同一位声优的演绎，但事实就是如此。飞田展男利用发音位置的变化控制声音效果，再辅以气声和力度，塑造出截然相反类型的人物。从控制发音变化的技巧来说，飞田展男是独一无二的。","career":["seiyu"],"id":4167,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":102504},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/d4/70/131628_crt_4JDf4.jpg?r=1731049791","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/d4/70/131628_crt_4JDf4.jpg?r=1731049791","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/d4/70/131628_crt_4JDf4.jpg?r=1731049791","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/d4/70/131628_crt_4JDf4.jpg?r=1731049791"},"name":"Ironhide","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/9e/0b/4614_prsn_qQyu9.jpg?r=1573408993","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/9e/0b/4614_prsn_qQyu9.jpg?r=1573408993","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/9e/0b/4614_prsn_qQyu9.jpg?r=1573408993","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/9e/0b/4614_prsn_qQyu9.jpg?r=1573408993"},"name":"遊佐浩二","short_summary":"","career":["seiyu"],"id":4614,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":